      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and the variable M differential lock for precise power distribution. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed to ensure mechanical longevity, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers that preserve the original suspension geometry. While the paint displays minor road-going patina, the internals are top-tier, featuring recent rod bearing service and a high-efficiency cooling system. A mechanically robust specimen ready for spirited canyon carving or track day duty.",
